00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:01,960
Thinking that words like romance, love

413
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:04,640
don’t seem to fit me.

414
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:08,750
I used to think the same.

415
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:11,400
I told myself

416
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,070
those things can’t make money

417
00:21:14,070 --> 00:21:15,200
or get results,

418
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:16,030
