419
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,160
But today I realized

420
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:21,790
it’s not that I don't want them,

421
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:23,790
it’s that I can’t.

422
00:21:25,030 --> 00:21:26,550
So I convinced myself that I don't want

423
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:27,270
